params.text:
Customer Lifetime Value is important for companies because higher the numbers, greater the profits. It is 5-25 times easier to retain or grow a customer than to acquire one. New startups on the block need to design customer acquisition strategies from existing companies. Your channel, your implementation, your marketing - all and more matter when designing your strategies,

 The template is for teams to brainstorm on what possible strategies they can have for acquiring customers, retaining them, or getting more value out of them.

params.text:
* The template consists of filler text beforehand to get the team started on thinking. 
* The team choses a facilitator and assigned each member a sticker and a voting dot. 
* Prior to starting, the members brainstorm on the categories. As soon as the timer is started they start joting down their ideas and placing them in the correct category.
* Now the facilitator starts a voting session to have the team members vote on the best suggested strategies. 
* The top 5 are noted and places in the board below to signal what strategies need to be worked on. Happy brainstorming!
